<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mondiale di Tennis</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background: #0b1d2a;
      color: white;
    }

    header {
      background: #132f4c;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    nav {
      background: #0f253a;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      margin: 0 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #132f4c;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    🎾 Mondiale di Tennis con i Dadi
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">Classifica</a>
    <a href="#">Tornei</a>
    <a href="#">Video</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="card">
      <div class="title">Benvenuto</div>
      <p>Questo è il Mondiale di Tennis simulato con i dadi. 32 giocatori, 28 settimane, tornei ATP 250, 500, Master 1000 e Slam.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="title">Ultimo torneo</div>
      <p>In arrivo...</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="title">Prossimi eventi</div>
      <p>Calendario in aggiornamento.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
